\par\pard\plain \tx0\tx360\tx720\tx1080\tx1440\tx1800\tx2160\tx2880\tx3600\tx4320\fi360\sa120\sl264\slmult1\ql\ltrch\loch {\f0\fs28\b0\i0 Laura was anxiously waiting for Evan to arrive. He didn\loch\af0\hich\af0\dbch\af0\uc1\u8217\'92t want to come over until he was certain Maggie was busy working the dinner rush. For his plan to work, there had to be no chance Maggie would walk in during his conversation with Laura.}
\par\plain {\f0\fs28\b0\i0 Laura watched through the window as Evan parked his car. She had the door already open when he arrived. Laura closed the door after Evan entered and proceeded to whack him in the arm.}
\par\plain {\f2\fs28\b1\cf5 <$Scr_Cs::1>Laura: <!$Scr_Cs::1>}{\f0\fs28\b0\i0\cf6 Laura said, \loch\af0\hich\af0\dbch\af0\uc1\u8220\'93That\u8217\'92s for making me wait all week without telling me anything!\u8221\'94}
\par\plain {\f0\fs28\b0\i0\cf6 Evan laughed and said, \loch\af0\hich\af0\dbch\af0\uc1\u8220\'93I didn\u8217\'92t want to say anything until I was sure we could pull it off.\u8221\'94}
\par\plain {\f2\fs28\b1\i0\cf5 <$Scr_Cs::1>Laura: <!$Scr_Cs::1>}{\f0\fs28\b0\i0\cf6 \loch\af0\hich\af0\dbch\af0\uc1\u8220\'93We? Pull what off?\u8221\'94 asked Laura.}
\par\plain {\f0\fs28\b0\i0 They walked to the kitchen table, and Evan pulled out his laptop and started it up.}
\par\plain {\f2\fs28\b1\i0\cf5 <$Scr_Cs::1>Evan: <!$Scr_Cs::1>}{\f0\fs28\b0\i0\cf6 \loch\af0\hich\af0\dbch\af0\uc1\u8220\'93I am going to need your help with this, but I have to warn you we may have to lower our standards of integrity and stretch the truth a bit. Are you up for that?\u8221\'94 asked Evan.}
\par\plain {\f2\fs28\b1\i0\cf5 <$Scr_Cs::1>Laura: <!$Scr_Cs::1>}{\f0\fs28\b0\i0\cf6 \loch\af0\hich\af0\dbch\af0\uc1\u8220\'93Will it keep Maggie in school?\u8221\'94}
\par\plain {\f2\fs28\b1\i0\cf5 <$Scr_Cs::1>Evan: <!$Scr_Cs::1>}{\f0\fs28\b0\i0\cf6 \loch\af0\hich\af0\dbch\af0\uc1\u8220\'93Not only that, but it will help cover her monthly expenses, so she won\u8217\'92t have to work more hours.\u8221\'94}
\par\plain {\f2\fs28\b1\i0\cf5 <$Scr_Cs::1>Laura: <!$Scr_Cs::1>}{\f0\fs28\b0\i0\cf6 \loch\af0\hich\af0\dbch\af0\uc1\u8220\'93Then, I\u8217\'92ll do whatever it takes,\u8221\'94 said Laura.}
